  title="Gesture Seat Height Range for Tall People | Tall Chair Advisor"
  description="Steelcase Gesture seat height range is 16&quot;–21&quot; (standard cylinder). Recommended settings by height for 6'0&quot;–6'5&quot;, how to adjust, and how it compares to the Aeron and Leap Plus."
  ogType="article"
  schema={schema}
>
